name: CSS Critic Examples
tagline: Helping you set up CSS Critic with your project
body: Helping you set up CSS Critic with your project =============================================== Integrating [CSS Critic](http://cburgmer.github.io/csscritic/) into your project isn't difficult. But it helps to have an example to look at, doesn't it? Examples ======== Here's a list of examples currently featured here: - [Vanilla JavaScript](vanillajs/) (just plain JavaScript, no framework needed) built on [TodoMVC](https://github.com/tastejs/todomvc/tree/gh-pages/vanilla-examples/vanillajs) - [Angular JS](angularjs/) built on [TodoMVC](https://github.com/tastejs/todomvc/tree/gh-pages/architecture-examples/angularjs) Licensed under MIT.
